{"tid":948765,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男偷電動車電瓶被電死　法院判車主要賠22萬","createTime":"2018-12-20T10:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T07:15:19.000Z","uid":150609,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"97537da43c4b92a790cb1beeaf5fcbc78cda803b","tid":948765,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4KFGqbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4KFGqbc.jpg&h=a8d7afdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻攝自《北京青年報》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國一名男子將電動車停在樓下，小偷在偷電坪的時候意外觸電亡，法院判車主要賠償小偷5萬人民幣(約22萬新台幣)。<br />\n<br />\n據《北京青年報》報導，中國武漢一名劉姓車主，將電動車放在樓下充電，而小偷看上了這輛電動車，上前準備把電瓶偷走，沒想到偷在偷電瓶時意外觸電身亡。下大雨，電瓶漏電把小偷電死了。<br />\n<br />\n事發後<span style=\"color: gold;\">小偷家屬向劉先生索賠20萬人民幣(約88萬新台幣)賠償金。最後經法院調解，車主賠償5萬塊錢的精神損失費。</span>（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29fbc827110edbcd5be2b082a549e2f702807a0a","tid":948765,"uid":193642,"like":48,"dislike":6,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:07:08.000Z","msg":"某程度上車主要多謝個小偷, 因為無小偷嘅話車主已經電死左"},{"pid":"3fd152d60d32fbfa95d03c5c0eedc575747921c0","tid":948765,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:07:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e77fdf350ae0e5d9ece8ac1166449ca358f697a7","tid":948765,"uid":150609,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"29fbc827110edbcd5be2b082a549e2f702807a0a","tid":948765,"uid":193642,"like":48,"dislike":6,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:07:08.000Z","msg":"某程度上車主要多謝個小偷, 因為無小偷嘅話車主已經電死左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:08:47.000Z","msg":"點會.. 佢係叉緊電果陣偷個電瓶<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5ee40b962eb3a001c2ee243c19cf5e3b870727","tid":948765,"uid":19932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:15:11.000Z","msg":"值，五萬一條一命"},{"pid":"6745d78475d5be3c2db57ea115c039cf224eec7e","tid":948765,"uid":1575