class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T13:12:13.000Z","msg":"根本就唔合理  就算係佢疏忽令到舊電本身危險  都係法院罰佢錢  點都唔會賠比個家屬啦<br />\n依家係助長犯法行為喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T00:22:03.000Z","msg":"冇關係<br />\n個小偷觸摸電動車既動機同電動車係室外落雨差電導致漏電既危險性冇衝突，就算係美國發生依然判到車主要賠償，而且賠更多<br />\n因為美國有懲罰性賠償，食個m記自己on9倒瀉咖啡辣親都可以告到m記賠50萬美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14795ea9a36279eac77e12fb4999810eb061e8b0","tid":948765,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T10:54:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.whzy.hbfy.gov.cn/DocManage/ViewDoc?docId=e24dcaaf-33d2-4115-a972-6e3be7256f83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.whzy.hbfy.gov.cn%2FDocManage%2FViewDoc%3FdocId%3De24dcaaf-33d2-4115-a972-6e3be7256f83&d=zyCA%2FeMUyPGN4KpnIxyjdxxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=66ed1d5d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.whzy.hbfy.gov.cn/DocManage/ViewDoc?docId=e24dcaaf-33d2-4115-a972-6e3be7256f83</a><br />\n<em><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">情況通報<br />\n我市兩級法院沒有受理過媒體所報導、評述的<br />\n充電電瓶車被盜觸電身亡賠償案</div></strong><br />\n發佈時間： 2018-12-20 20:51:34<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;近日，有媒體報導稱，有人在盜竊我市劉先生停放在樓下充電的電動車時，意外觸電身亡，&ldquo;小偷家屬&rdquo;向劉先生索賠20萬賠償金；經法院調解，車主賠償&ldquo;小偷家屬&rdquo;5萬元精神損失費。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;媒體報導後，我市兩級法院高度重視，立即對媒體報導、評述的&ldquo;案件&rdquo;進行了認真的梳理和核查。<span style=\"color: red;\">經查，我市兩級法院近年來沒有受理過媒體所報導、評述的相關案件或類似案件。我們注意到，報導該&ldquo;案件&rdquo;的首發媒體已自行刪除了相關文章。</span><br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;武漢兩級法院感謝媒體、讀者和網民對法院工作的關心、監督和支持；同時，我們將與媒體、讀者和網民一起共同抵制虛假信息，共同維護良好網絡空間。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;武漢市中級人民法院<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2018年12月20日</em>"},{"pid":"a527fc60c38ae93c474c100325084c49b63c1c39","tid":948765,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T07:15:19.000Z","msg":"死大陸仔！"}]}